HEADWORD: irradiancy
<hw>ir*ra"di*an*cy</hw> <pr>(⟦icr⟧r*r⟦amac⟧"d⟦icr⟧*⟦ait⟧n*s⟦ycr⟧)</pr>,
}</mhw> <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From <er>irradiant</er>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of irradiating; emission of rays of
light.</def>⟦br⟧
