<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>That which irradiates or is irradiated; luster;
splendor; irradiation; brilliancy.</def> <rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>irradiant</ent>⟦br⟧
